name: 2014 Diary by Kate Knapp Twigseeds
description:
A parade of feathery and furry creatures live inside, bursting with beautifully illustrated characters by Kate Knapp, along with delightful and wise inspirational quotes. Travel along the precious days, weeks and months of 2014. Share in the delight and wisdom of Twigseeds' irresistible philosophers. Chart your life, daily insights, reflections, cherished moments and fond memories.
Hard cover, 160 pages 148 x 190 mm, Eco-friendly, wood free matt paper.

name: Twigseeds Everlasting Calendar illustrated by Kate Knapp
description:
... for birthdays and anniversaries of your favourite flock...
Record the birthdays and anniversaries of your closest offspring and kindred spirits. With quivering whiskers and wagging tails, the vivacious characters inside share their wisdom and insight with you each day, all year round.
Spiral bound Perpetual Calendar 125 x 280 mm
14 pages
Eco-friendly paper

name: "RUBY RED SHOES GOES TO PARIS" children's picture book
description:
Ruby and her grandmother Babushka are off to Paris for a holiday! When they arrive they go and meet Babushka′s brother, Monsieur Gaspar Galushka, who loves hats as much as Ruby loves red shoes. And with Monsieur is his grandson, Felix, who becomes Ruby′s guide while she is in Paris. Together the two young hares zip around Paris on Felix′s racy red scooter taking in all of the beautiful sights that Paris has to offer. It is the adventure of a lifetime, filled with memories that Ruby will treasure forever.
Trimsize: 230 x 163 mm; Pages: 48; Ages:4-8
Available NOW

name: RUBY RED SHOES children's picture book by Kate Knapp
description:
This is Kate Knapp's first picture book in the Ruby Red Shoes series.
Hard cover, 48 pages, 238 x 172 x 13 mm

Ruby Red Shoes lives in a colourful caravan with her grandmother. Ruby is gentle and kind and cares for all living things, including plants and trees, animals and people.
Ruby is also particularly fond of strawberry jam and peppermint tea.
Ages: 4+

name: RUBY RED SHOES soft plush toy by Twigseeds
description:
Designed in Australia by Twigseeds.
Ruby Red Shoes plush toy … the softest aware hare you’ll ever meet. With the softest of fur, the Ruby Red Shoes plush toy is irresistible to snuggle with and tell all your stories and secrets to! 

Approximate height 40cm
Conforms to Australian and New Zealand safety standards Suitable for ages 0 months and over.

name: Guest Book illustrated by Kate Knapp - Twigseeds
description:
A GATHERING OF GUESTS
Delighted guests will flock to write their heartfelt messages, chirp a happy hello or tweet a rapturous review. Enter a truly magical world where parades of curious characters leap, bounce and wing their way into your imagination!
Hard Cover 210 x 148 mm  Illustrated by Kate Knapp
172 Pages; Eco-friendly, wood free matt paper.

name: Australian Swans Giclee Print
description:
Giclee Print by artist: Leslie van der Sluys (1939-2010)
The paper size is A3 (42 x 29.7 cm). Rectangular format image size is 25 x 31 cm, square 25 x 25 cm, notwithstanding one oversize image at 38 x 25 cm. 

With Leslie van der Sluys’ passing in 2010, his much loved hand-coloured linoprints are now no longer available. In response his partner and photographer Christopher Sanders, manager of Leslie van der Sluys’ estate has released a selection of ten classic van der Sluys images from the early 1980s through to 2009 as high quality reproductions.

Reproduction quality is achieved by using archival matt Museo Portfolio Rag paper. This heavyweight fine art paper approximates the feel and quality of the original Velin Arches used with the originals.
